data.description: Welcome to your new home in the highly sought-after Kingsview! This exquisite single-family home offers spacious and comfortable living with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a host of luxurious features that make it truly exceptional. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that seamlessly blends modern elegance with classic charm. The open-concept design allows for effortless flow between the living spaces, perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The heart of this home is the spacious gourmet kitchen, featuring Black appliances, Stone countertops, ample storage, and a center island that's perfect for meal prep and casual dining. Perfect for  hosting a family dinner and Friends, this kitchen will meet your expectations. The spacious primary suite is a true sanctuary, complete with his and her closet, Vaulted Ceiling  and a spa-like ensuite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Finished basement  with a walk out to the Paver Deck with fire pit.. Step outside to your oasis backing up to beautiful trees. Other features include  two-car garage, laundry room,  ample storage, hard wood flooring, crown molding, chair rail, ceiling fans,  10 foot ceiling in basement. You must see for you self.   PLEASE REMOVE YOUR SHOES
